kibanaSavedObjectMeta.searchSourceJSON:
{"query":{"esql":"from logs-apps* | RENAME app_name as App
| RENAME log_level as Nivel
| RENAME message as Mensaje
| EVAL Nivel = CASE(
    Nivel == "T", "TRACE",
    Nivel == "TRACE", "TRACE",
    Nivel == "D", "DEBUG",
    Nivel == "DEBUG", "DEBUG",
    Nivel == "I", "INFO",
    Nivel == "INFO", "INFO",
    Nivel == "W", "WARNING",
    Nivel == "WARNING", "WARNING",
    Nivel == "E", "ERROR",
    Nivel == "ERROR", "ERROR",
    "Null")
| SORT @timestamp DESC
| LIMIT 500"},"index":{"id":"97661b02-3e1d-4ee1-8e45-7e4405ee4777","title":"logs-apps*","timeFieldName":"@timestamp","sourceFilters":[],"fieldFormats":{},"runtimeFieldMap":{},"allowNoIndex":false,"name":"logs-apps*","allowHidden":false},"filter":[]}
